        },
        "text_y6dkGq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>HARAMOON stood out to us as a Korean beauty brand that aligns with our values — no BS, science-backed, and focused on foundational skin barrier health.  Tired of trends that felt more like empty promises, HARAMOON became our skin's true friend.</p><p>Now, we want to share that with as many people who are eager to try the growing wave of Korean skincare brands available in the US. We are confident you won't be disappointed.</p><p>Whether you’re dealing with stress, dehydration, or sensitivity, HARAMOON offers more than a quick fix — gentle enough to be used separately or hasten results by using multiple together. </p>"
          }
        },
        "button_WmxBmj": {
